2015-12-24 12-00-00:
	Title: Happy Holidays! The release is out!
	Author: Oliver Brakmann
	Content: For Christmas, the OpenRA developers give you a brand-new shiny OpenRA release!\n\nIt has a new global chat, re-designed server browser and lobby, "joystick" scrolling, Defend stance by default for units, a completely re-balanced Dune 2000 mod, improved balancing, bugfixes and many things more!\n\nHead over to our website at http://openra.net to read the full release announcement, and see the complete unabridged list of new features, improvements and fixes at http://changelog.openra.net.\n\nHave fun, and Merry Christmas to all!
